    <font color="#9f3215" face="verdana" size="2">The centaur archer is a fairly dangerous enemy if encountered when you are on bad footing with the centaurs.  Killing them will only make matters worse due to the faction hits.  If you are a particularly evil individual or are in with the evil factions, you might want to avoid South Karana until level 25 or so.</font></td>
